[SN]TITLE[SN]
Girl in critical condition after being hit by car in Dundee

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An eight-year-old girl is in a critical condition after being hit by a car in Dundee.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident involving a black Ford Ka happened on St Fillans Road at about 21:00 on Saturday.
The girl is being treated at Ninewells Hospital in Dundee.
Police have asked for anyone who may have witnessed the collision, or who saw a black Ford Ka in the area at the time, to come forward.
